rawContent:
I see the lights of the city-
You fail to see in front of you-
That the light in my eyes-
Died and has gone cold.

I try to follow the beat-
And act as if I'm still alive-
But we both know now-
That I'm tired and this drags on.
#poetry #depression #SuicidePrevention #sad #tired
